sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    participant Controller as KServe Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant KnativeAPI as Knative Serving API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Storage as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Transformer as Transformer Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS

    Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: Model Deployment via InferenceService

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>TLS 1.2+ mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation Result
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>TLS 1.2+ mTLS
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated InferenceService (defaults injected)
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

    Note over Controller: Controller watches InferenceService CR
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET InferenceService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: InferenceService spec
    Controller->>KnativeAPI: Create Knative Service<br/>ServiceAccount Token TLS1.2+
    KnativeAPI-->>Controller: Knative Service created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Istio VirtualService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: VirtualService created

    Note over Storage,Predictor: storage-initializer downloads model
    Predictor->>Storage: GET /models/model-v1<br/>AWS IAM / GCP Service Account TLS1.2+
    Storage-->>Predictor: Model artifacts downloaded

    Note over Client,Transformer: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless Mode)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS1.2+ Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Activator: Forward request HTTP mTLS<br/>Service Identity validation

    alt Transformer configured
        Activator->>Transformer: Pre-process request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
        Transformer->>Predictor: Forward to predictor<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
        Predictor-->>Transformer: Prediction result
        Transformer->>Transformer: Post-process response
        Transformer-->>Activator: Final response
    else No transformer
        Activator->>Predictor: Inference request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
        Predictor-->>Activator: Prediction result
    end

    Activator-->>Gateway: Response HTTP mTLS
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over Client,Predictor: Flow 3: InferenceGraph Multi-Step Routing

    participant Router as Router Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Step1 as Step 1 InferenceService<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Step2 as Step 2 InferenceService<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS

    Client->>Router: POST /v1/graph/predict<br/>Bearer Token mTLS
    Router->>Step1: Step 1 request<br/>Propagated Headers mTLS
    Step1-->>Router: Step 1 response
    Router->>Step2: Step 2 request<br/>Propagated Headers mTLS
    Step2-->>Router: Step 2 response
    Router-->>Client: Final aggregated response

    Note over Controller,Predictor: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor

    Prometheus->>Controller: GET /metrics 8080/TCP HTTP<br/>None (NetworkPolicy restricted)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Controller metrics
    Prometheus->>Predictor: GET /metrics 8080/TCP or 9090/TCP HTTP<br/>ServiceMonitor scraping
    Predictor-->>Prometheus: Inference metrics
